docs.text: Welcome to DiscordBotExt DiscordBotExt is the extensions developed based on discord.py bots. Due to the sake of compatibility, a mainframe is developed too. Required packages -pip install discord -pip install chinese_converter -pip install discord-webhook -pip install mwclient -pip install fuzzywuzzy -pip install flask -pip install discord-py-slash-command Extensions admin baro common event logup OrphixRank rivenPrice wfm wiki worldState
